# Principle 10 (Right Backup Strategy) - Dated backup before rm -rf or sed modifications
# Principle 14 (Interactive vs Non-Interactive) - Respects FORCE_REINSTALL and non-TTY safely
# Principle 16 (Input Pattern Checking) - Validates PROJECT_DIR and FORCE flag
#
# CRITICAL DEFENSIVE RULES:
# 1. Never assume ${PROJECT_DIR} is empty or safe to delete.
